Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}虚有其表  无法生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:16.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}光靠温柔  何以治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:22.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}这一成不变的世界中  是什么被夺走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:28.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}色彩之歌中  你听到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:32.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Everything is bright
